# Pulse Controls
super + {Up, Down}
    pulsevolctrl "output-vol" "alsa_output.pci-0000_00_1f.3.analog-stereo" {+2%, -2%}

super + m
    pulsevolctrl "output-mute" "alsa_output.pci-0000_00_1f.3.analog-stereo"

